                        <p><img src="~/img/data/abilities/seal-defense.png" title="Seal Defense" style="width: 3vw;" /><b>Seal Defense</b><br /><i>If unit damages foe during combat, foe suffers DEF -6 for 1 turn after combat.</i></p>
